## Userinfo Module - English
userinfo-me-updated = ✅ Your info has been updated!
userinfo-me-empty = ℹ️ You haven't set any info about yourself yet! Use /setme <text>
userinfo-me-empty-other = ℹ️ This user hasn't set any info about themselves yet.
userinfo-bio-updated = ✅ Updated {$name}'s bio!
userinfo-bio-empty = ℹ️ You don't have a bio set yet! Someone needs to reply to you with /setbio <text>
userinfo-bio-empty-other = ℹ️ This user doesn't have a bio set yet.
userinfo-bio-self = ❌ You can't set your own bio! You're at the mercy of others here...
userinfo-bio-reply-required = ❌ Reply to someone's message to set their bio!
userinfo-too-long = ❌ Text must be under {$max} characters! You have {$len}.
